    <div id="home_message">
     <h1>Welcome&nbsp;</h1> 
     <p> We are a long-established Department within the University of Cambridge, where we offer world-class <a href="teaching">teaching</a> courses, carry out innovative and forward-thinking <a href="research">research</a>, and provide excellent <a href="resources/facilities">facilities</a> in a dynamic and inclusive environment. </p> 
     <div id="admissions_box"> 
      <div> 
       <p> Do you want to study here? </p> 
       <p> We offer courses across the spectrum of the Earth Sciences. We have <a href="admissions">lots of information</a> about those courses, and about being a student in this Department.....&nbsp; </p> 
      </div> 
     </div> 
